:0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:48:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>期指281個陣掃左三萬蚊 近牛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽日落多一浸就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n死哂，最097<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5a793ab6a1372759f421b7674b8de9f68f4216","tid":440871,"uid":21331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:49:16.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71367caf7b9b2b9b061fb9bfaf34e88397acb78","tid":440871,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T13:06:57.000Z","msg":"出黎做野都淨係敢買正股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e2c9bba23672f2295acee4341ef4b741ebe199","tid":440871,"uid":42229,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T13:12:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學生哥未有穩定收入<br />\n就用學費grant loan黎賭先駛未來錢<br />\n仲要買牛熊未學行先學走<br />\n<br />\n你每個決定都係踩緊鋼線邊緣<br />\n完全無承受風險嘅能力就學人玩到咁大<br />\n如日後繼續咁大膽<br />\n你遲早all-in去跳樓自殺都唔掂<br />\n<br />\n忠言逆耳<br />\n你想進步就要知衰</blockquote><br />\n都唔係咁講 當年用loan學人玩細價老千股 輸左一萬 之後知驚唔再玩<br />\n如果以前冇試過 出到黎做野先拎成份糧成份儲蓄玩 輸得仲甘"},{"pid":"b51df178e9743b9be26255c40f328f1520be854b","tid":440871,"uid":144113,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T13:23:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係學生  有6位數都唔敢玩牛熊 <br />\n你仲拎學費黎玩  抵撚死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傻仔，人地可能係蠢但係夠膽使錢，佢未跳樓既話我欣賞佢<br />\n你連掂下都唔夠膽就無謂話人抵死啦<br />\n講到自己有6位數好似好威咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477ff6e313fb89a9a2e9ff11c294453225c8672b","tid":440871,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T13:26:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>學生哥未有穩定收入<br />\n就用學費grant loan黎賭先駛未來錢<br />\n仲要買牛熊未學行先學走<br />\n<br />\n你每個決定都係踩緊鋼線邊緣<br />\n完全無承受風險嘅能力就學人玩到咁大<br />\n如日後繼續咁大膽<br />\n你遲早all-in去跳樓自殺都唔掂<br />\n<br />\n忠言逆耳<br />\n你想進步就要知衰</blockquote><br />\n都唔係咁講 當年用loan學人玩細價老千股 輸左一萬 之後知驚唔再玩<br />\n如果以前冇試過 出到黎做野先拎成份糧成份儲蓄玩 輸得仲甘</blockquote><br />\n其實係好事, 第一次唔輸過第時點會玩得更好<br />\n最緊要檢討自己點解輸"},{"pid":"fe43862d5a8757e2e4994e1b51c395abb1e204d4","tid":440871,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T13:28:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091c700be927771d4f352d7916eff4ab41304e16","tid":440871,"uid":131298,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T13:28:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>學生哥未有穩定收入<br />\n就用學費grant loan黎賭先駛未來錢<br />\n仲要買牛熊未學行先學走<br />\n<br />\n你每個決定都係踩緊鋼線邊緣<br />\n完全無承受風險嘅能力就學人玩到咁大<br />\n如日後繼續咁大膽<br />\n你遲早all-in去跳樓自殺都唔掂<br />\n<br />\n忠言逆耳<br />\n你想進步就要知衰</blockquote><br />\n都唔係咁講 當年用loan學人玩細價老千股 輸左一萬 之後知驚唔再玩<br />\n如果以前冇試過 出到黎做野先拎成份糧成份儲蓄玩 輸得仲甘</blockquote><br />\n其實係好事, 第一次唔輸過第時點會玩得更好<br />\n最緊要檢討自己點解輸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n賭錢輸邊有得檢討，只有唔玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58574df39247465bccde4fbba154ff388aa70b3a","tid":440871,"uid":353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T13:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590e9fc9a2e58482c257b45f58b2b7fc33f0a48d","tid":440871,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"